Manually Add LLM Model
Download the LLM binary manually:

Go to: https://gpt4all.io/models/ggml-gpt4all-j-v1.3-groovy.bin

Place it in: models/ggml-gpt4all-j-v1.3-groovy.bin

Add your PDF
Place a PDF named example.pdf in the documents/ folder.

Run the App
streamlit run app.py

Folder Structure
biomed-chatbot/
├── app.py
├── download_model.py
├── documents/
│   └── example.pdf
├── models/
│   ├── all-MiniLM-L6-v2/
│   └── ggml-gpt4all-j-v1.3-groovy.bin

Ideal Use Cases
Healthcare research Q&A

Offline hospital systems

Secure environments with no internet
